Description
Mah-Jomino blends the challenge of Mahjong & Dominoes into a
unique two-sided mahjong game.
For the past decade, archaeologist William McEndri has
dedicated his life to locating the twelve ancient artifacts
that could prove the existence of the lost city of Atlantis.
The time has come for his daughter Helen to carry on his
adventure. Journey with Helen into the unknown in this truly
exciting Mahjong experience.
